@old_middle
subtitle: This demographic is fiercely reactionary and anti-syndicalist. Expect fierce opposition, including reaction from other political parties...

The Old Middle Class has been one of the SPD's grand oppositions. It's unlikely we'll manage to make inroads...

- @black_monday_harassment: Hm? Black Monday has caused an epidemic of suicides among this class?...This is a great opportunity. We'll begin a campaign of harassment and blame these idiots, under financial and mental pressure, we can maybe get them to finally jump out of bridges.
- @monarchist: Let's do a pro-monarchy campaign. Social Democracy and a People's Kaiser under the German Flag!
- @patriotic: We'll aim for a patriotic campaign, presenting the SPD as a defender of the German Monarchy and lauding our accomplishments for the nation! We will prove how we are NOT Syndicalists!
- @economy: What these guys really care about is the economy. We must show them how free market liberalism is inferior to state intervention, spreading information about our economic proposals and accomplishments.
- @peace_branch: If we want to make in-roads with the old middle class, we'll need an effort from the bottom. We must extend a peace branch from our grassroots, undoing old rivalries and building up community ties, until we can eventually show how the true enemies are the Junkers.
- @start: Let's check the other demographics.

